--------------
  Installing
--------------

On XP systems:
	
	Rename
	C:\Program Files\Cumulus\web
	to
	C:\Program Files\Cumulus\OldWeb
	
	Copy the web folder in this download to
	C:\Program Files\Cumulus\web
	
	Start/Restart Cumulus
	
On Vista systems:

	Rename
	C:\Users\[username]\AppData\Local\VirtualStore\Program Files\Cumulus\web
	to
	C:\Users\[username]\AppData\Local\VirtualStore\Program Files\Cumulus\OldWeb
	
	Copy the web folder in this download to
	C:\Users\[username]\AppData\Local\VirtualStore\Program Files\Cumulus\web
	
	Start/Restart Cumulus
	
--------------
  Modification
--------------

	Out of the box the theme comes with a logo for "Oxford Weather Station" you can change this by creating a new logo the whole theme is included in Adobe CS3 PSD format.
	
	Its also been made simple to create a background image by using the background.psd file.